channel.title: [rs377d] Subsonic v1.5 ~ #377
channel.description:
[b] [/b][img]http://img716.imageshack.us/img716/986/icpg.png[/img]
Even after 2 years, I still haven't seen any project that was based off an [b]rs377d[/b].. So yeah, I've came back to RSPS and I wanted my first release to be cool and based by a [b]cool protocol and base[/b].. so yeah here it is. I've released the v1 like two years ago, and here finally the v1.5 I guess. There's a lot of work to do on this still, but it's sexy and I hope that there will be atleast some downloads. It already allows [b]full screen interfaces [/b]so yeah, the great welcome screen it's already there, as in the v1. :)
I haven't really spent much time on this, I was just having some good fun making something new out of this heh.
Here's the content:
[ul][li][size=1]Login Screen(Welcome Screen)[/size][/li] [li][size=1]Skills[/size][/li] [li][size=1]Arrow Hints[/size][/li] [li][size=1]Object Arrow Hints[/size][/li] [li][size=1]Logout - Thanks Scully![/size][/li] [li][size=1]Command handling system[/size][/li] [li][size=1]XP skills[/size][/li] [li][size=1]Action button handling[/size][/li] [li][size=1]Animations[/size][/li] [li][size=1]Graphic system[/size][/li] [li][size=1]Lot of new packets[/size][/li] [li][size=1]Commands actually work now[/size][/li] [li][size=1]Most of the opcodes[/size][/li] [li][size=1]Run energy (loads by logging in with an acc, needs decreasing)[/size][/li] [li][size=1]Running [/size][/li] [li][size=1]Added Object and NPC event listeners, needs to add the definitions[/size][/li][/ul] It's very nicely handled and it's great to work with, you can learn a lot by using this as your base.. This was released by [b]Blakeman8192 [/b]like 3 years ago, and there's barely someone who is using this.. Few people asked me for the v1 Subsonic, so I promised them to release a v1.5 and here it is. I hope you'll enjoy it :)
Here's the sexy welcome screen that I guess everybode like. [img]http://img189.imageshack.us/img189/6348/loginscreenp.png[/img]
As I've said I haven't spent much time on this, it was quite fun but I have still other things to do like school and bs like that so I just don't have a lot of time to spend on RSPS, I guess. Yeah I'm still working on the 194, I'm just having a break :)
[img]http://imageshack.us/a/img197/484/lzwl.png[/img] This is what message you get by clicking on the NPC (picture down, only to show it works) Object's and NPC's needs the definitions! [img]http://img853.imageshack.us/img853/631/qe0k.png[/img]
Running works now, just need to add the decreasing by running :) [img]http://img28.imageshack.us/img28/7557/8pqh.png[/img]
Take your time, and make something good out of this! [img]http://img32.imageshack.us/img32/6702/animz.png[/img]
[url=http://uppit.com/3mx7rq3tgoz9/Subsonic_v1.5.rar]Download Source[/url]
